frames.caption: A towering, fiery figure stands amidst a cosmic backdrop, its form crackling with energy. Surrounding it are celestial bodies and streams of light, creating a dramatic and otherworldly scene. The ground below appears molten, with glowing fissures spreading across its surface.

frames.description: The scene depicts a fantastical cosmic setting where a giant, dark entity stands amidst a starry backdrop. The environment is otherworldly, with celestial elements and energy flows adding to the mystical atmosphere.
